{"tid":905473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"意大利研究：有錢人成功是因為幸運","createTime":"2018-11-17T06:58:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T07:58:03.000Z","uid":122,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8f8ab383a813c23e36f589be56bbdeab01b60b0a","tid":905473,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T06:58:17.000Z","msg":"成功需苦幹，相信好多人都成日聽呢啲勉勵人嘅說話，覺得只要努力，自己一定可脫穎而出，成為有錢人。可惜事實總係殘酷，成為有錢人嘅原因，大部分都係因為幸運？<br />\n<br />\n根據意大利卡坦妮亞大學一項超過40年嘅追蹤調查，發現最富有嘅人入面，基本上全部都係靠父蔭或家庭而致富，另一少部分就係靠中獎得超級幸運成分；而佢哋嘅智商、技能都無特別比其他人優勝；反觀另一班無父幹嘅朋友，縱使有高學歷而智力高，但40年之後財富仍然不及「幸運」一班嘅一半。所以結論係，就算你幾努力幾醒幾叻都好，一樣係輸在起跑線呢！"},{"pid":"369f3adbb8e21227c40b839065d68d8f42caa25e","tid":905473,"uid":25560,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T07:02:51.000Z","msg":"一命二運三風水四積陰德五讀書"},{"pid":"bf088c99ab5a4ce7afb3ba837c944e29d4e468fc","tid":905473,"uid":44074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T07:06:24.000Z","msg":"所以呢？"},{"pid":"515fa801fdcce51f739ba4683993b51cecd2a9b9","tid":905473,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T07:08:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8e769e0445969dced1b5ce8e0dc211667604c649","tid":905473,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T07:09:50.000Z","msg":"幸運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n父幹就父幹啦"},{"pid":"105ff2d5fdb36d688274e292561ec50f8ccade67","tid":905473,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T07:10:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5dced58903bf2003e80b7dd691f0c79d5bd80895","tid":905473,"uid":151933,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T07:10:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20110214/large/14la1p101.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.